                    "value": 2
                },
                "category": "offensive",
                "description": {
                    "value": "<p>The dragoons draw bows and fire arrows as a ranged attack. This volley is a @Template[type:burst|distance:10] within 80 feet that deals @Damage[4d8[piercing]|options:area-damage] damage (@Check[reflex|dc:25|basic] save). When the troop is reduced to 2 or fewer segments, this area decreases to a @Template[type:burst|distance:5].</p>"
                },
